ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: open forum to discuss current research interests
It will be interesting to see how the new once/month and all-inclusive design works.
Yes, I will recommend this course to other students who will conduct research, as this course provides valuable information needed in research.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: Helped to progress my dissertation proposal.Ability to ask questions in a non-threatening environment helped to expand knowledge-base.

some knowledge cannot be learned from the course work, such as previous experiences of conducting research, problem solving and things that only can be learned from personal experience. those are sometimes really critical while doing research, as these knowledge could save your time and avoid preventable mistakes. i am glad that i learned a lot of this sore of knowledge in this course.
